data.description: Now also up For Rent! We would love to sell it, but seller has put it on the rental market as well. Come look at this White Rock Estates 2 story beauty on a corner lot. If you are looking for a large shop (large enough for a lift) for mechanic work, crafts, woodworking, then this is the place. There is a 2nd shed for all the yard equipment too. Need a place to park another vehicle or boat, we have that as well. The above ground pool has been closed down for the winter, but we have photos and video of when it was up and running. The screened in patio is perfect for relaxing, or sit on the open deck to get some sun. The corner lot has an extra curb cut to bring that project car into the large metal workshop. The rooms are large, the kitchen well designed with granite counter tops, and lots of counter space. You'll love the large pantry too! Call me or your realtor to set up a showing.
